{
  "stem": "3973.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I knew how to-- with the question of where to go, how to make sure that we find a place where there was water-- water, not to make noise, not to have-- to have the wind blowing in such a way that-- whatever, the various conditions of surviving in the woods.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I would sneak at night to steal fruit from-- off the trees, approaching from such a way that the dogs would not smell-- smell me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew all of these adventure stories not to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But it was-- this was not the way to be.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Something had to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How long can we stay in the woods?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, apparently, what has happened that time in the meadow changed my feeling towards my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Before, I was willing to die with her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now, as I-- going back many years later, I guess the feelings were somehow she betrayed me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At the same time, she saved my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I decided one day in the woods, totally without any preconceived ideas, I'm leaving.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was-- I told them that there were too much-- many of us, rather.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our chances of survival are limited.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm going to go to Krakow on my own.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And my mother tried to stop me, says that I bring them courage.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But whatever it was, I decided, no, I'm going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she, in her wisdom-- and it was always my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The father and my grandmother like didn't exist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In her wisdom, she decided that maybe this-- there's a chance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So this was the first time I put my long pants on, my father's pants.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
